T02TD3063E:119a-1: tsanda ma h'a ro sha na s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02TD3063E:119a-3: khro bo gtum po chen po'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02TD3063E:119a-4: bcom ldan 'das 'jam pa'i rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3063E:119a-5: pus mo sa la btsugs shing g-yas pa'i phyag na ral gri bsnams //
T02TD3063E:119a-6: de las gzhan pa'i phyag ni sdigs mdzub zhags pa dang 'brel zhing //
T02TD3063E:119a-7: sra zhing mkhregs pa'i sku mnga' nyi ma lta bur gtum pa'i spyan //
T02TD3063E:119a-8: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mi g-yo srid bgegs zhi byed shog / phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang ;
T02TD3063E:119a-9: / byang chub sems dpa' tshogs bcas pa //
T02TD3063E:119a-10: de la me tog la sogs pa'i //
T02TD3063E:119a-11: mchod pa la sogs blos byas nas //
T02TD3063E:119a-12: sems can sdug bsngal las bskyab phyir //
T02TD3063E:119a-13: bdag gi lus 'di dbul bar bya //
T02TD3063E:119a-14: dge ba 'phel phyir bsngags pa yis //
T02TD3063E:119a-15: sdig pa dag ni bshags par bya'o //
T02TD3063E:119b-0: @119b de nas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
T02TD3063E:119b-1: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang ni //
T02TD3063E:119b-2: slob ma slob sogs sems can gyi //
T02TD3063E:119b-3: bsod nams kun la rjes yi rang //
T02TD3063E:119b-4: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs song zhing //
T02TD3063E:119b-5: byang chub tu ni sems brtan nas //
T02TD3063E:119b-6: rim pa bzhin du tshangs pa'i gnas //
T02TD3063E:119b-7: bzhi po yang ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD3063E:119b-8: de'i mtshan bral bas stong pa ste //
T02TD3063E:119b-9: rgyu med pas na mtshan ma med //
T02TD3063E:119b-10: rang bzhin gyis ni dngos po rnams //
T02TD3063E:119b-11: sman pa dang ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD3063E:119b-12: de nas padma nyi dbus su //
T02TD3063E:119b-13: h'um las byung ba bsgom bya ste //
T02TD3063E:119b-14: dpa' bo spyan gnyis rab dmar zhing /
T02TD3063E:119b-15: phyag gnyis rin chen cod pan can ;
T02TD3063E:119b-16: / de ma thag tu sdig 'joms mgon //
T02TD3063E:119b-17: ji ltar 'dod pa rdzogs byed cing //
T02TD3063E:119b-18: aa tra si yi me tog mtshungs //
T02TD3063E:119b-20: tshems kyi mche bas ma mchu mnan //
T02TD3063E:119b-21: rgyan kun gyis ni rnam brgyan cing //
T02TD3063E:119b-22: g-yon pa sdigs mdzub zhags par ldan //
T02TD3063E:119b-23: phyag g-yas 'bar ba'i ral gris brel //
T02TD3063E:119b-24: pus mo sa la btsugs pa ni //
T02TD3063E:119b-25: 'jigs pa'i spyan rtsa bzlog pa yis //
T02TD3063E:119b-27: dam tshig sems dpa' lta bu yis //
T02TD3063E:119b-28: ye shes sems dpa' cher 'bar bsgom //
T02TD3063E:119b-29: de yi thugs kar sngags pa yis //
T02TD3063E:119b-30: mtshan ma sa bon bcas pa bsgom //
T02TD3063E:119b-31: skyon gsang sngags bzlas bya ste //
T02TD3063E:119b-32: lha yi rnam par sbyor bas so //
T02TD3063E:119b-33: de nas 'dod pa'i dngos grub ni //
T02TD3063E:119b-34: 'thob pa nyid du the tshom med //
T02TD3063E:119b-35: de la 'di ni gsang sngags rgyal //
T02TD3063E:119b-36: aom tsanda ma h'a ro sha na h'um phat /
T02TD3063E:119b-37: bdag gis bris pas gang thob pa //
T02TD3063E:119b-38: dge ba byang chub sgrub byed pa //
T02TD3063E:119b-40: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sgrub byed shog / khro bo gtum po'i sgrub thabs slob dpon dze t'a ri dgra las rnam par rgyal bas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3063E:119b-42: // / pandi ta su na ya shr'i dang /
T02TD3063E:119b-43: lo ts'a ba glog skya gzhon nu 'bar gyis bsgyur ba'o//
